reviewText: I was so glad to be able to order from American Empire DVD, I am satisfied with my purchase and how fast I got it.  Thank you so much and look forward to doing business again.  My DVD came packaged and protected so glad I ordered it.

This is a great DVD I enjoy it very much. it was great seenig Michael preform
and sing. I am glad that I got this. It also show you how the movie was made
and that was great footage also. If you do not have Captain EO you should buy it you will not waste your money.

Pat Minton  (Louisville, Ky.)
